User Stories

As a user, I want to enter unstructured ideas so that I can organize my thoughts easily.

Acceptance Criteria:

System accepts text input
Minimum 10 character required
Input is sent to backend controller
System responds within acceptable time


As a user, I want to answer clarification questions so that the system better understands my intent.

Acceptance Criteria:

Questions are generated only when input is submited
Questions appear in MCQ format 
Answers are merged with original input



As a user, I want enhanced visualization (colors, emojis) so that my mind map is more readable.

Acceptance Criteria:

Nodes include colors/emojis
Mind map renders correctly
All nodes visible
No broken layout

As a user, I want to view my mind map visually so that I can explore relationships between ideas and 
interactive diagram so that I can navigate large structures easily.

Acceptance Criteria:

clear relationships between nodes
Nodes can expand/collapse
Zoom and pan supported
Smooth interaction


As a user, I want to download my mind map as PNG, PDF and JSON.

Acceptance Criteria:

High-resolution image generated
Entire mind map captured
PDF generated with correct layout
Content readable in PDF
JSON downloadable
Matches schema with JSON format
Reusable structure of JSON
Download starts successfully


As a user, I want fast responses so that I don’t have to wait long.

Acceptance Criteria:

Clarification < 3s
Full generation within acceptable time < 10s

As a user, I want the system to handle invalid or empty input so that I don’t face errors.

Acceptance Criteria:

Errors shown clearly
System does not crash

As a user, I want to refine my input multiple times so that I can improve the output quality and 
consistent results so that I can rely on the system for repeated use.

Acceptance Criteria:

User can resubmit improved input
System regenerates output
Similar inputs produce similar outputs
Structure remains stable
